                  li Utilizes existing inlet, intermediate & outlet P/T ports
                  li 0-150 PSI range
                  li ±0.25% FS Accuracy
                  li Remote mounted
              .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-12
                p.product-2__sensor-card-title.product-2__sensor-card-title--secondary FCI Advantage:
                ul.product-2__sensor-card-list.product-2__sensor-card-list--marks
                  li Confirm system pressures, pressure independent operation & shutoff
                  li Provide feedback for pump control
                  li Develop real-time system pressure gradient

        .col-md-4
          .container(style="width: 100%;")
            .row.product-2__sensor-card.animate-40
              .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-12
